OL,3,CFrom Harry Potter to SpongeBob see how
OL,4,Cthe North West's marking World Book Day
OL,6,FChildren all over the North West have
OL,7,Fbeen joining the celebrations to mark
OL,8,FWorld Book Day, dressing up as
OL,9,Feverything from Harry Potter to
OL,10,FSpongeBob SquarePants!
OL,12,FThe international event is designed to
OL,13,Fencourage children to read, in an age
OL,14,Fwhen games and social media and
OL,15,Fscreens have lured them away.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
