OL,3,CFrom Harry Potter to SpongeBob see how
OL,4,Cthe North West's marking World Book Day
OL,6,FManchester United goalkeeper Senne
OL,7,FLammens joined in the fun with a visit
OL,8,Fon behalf of the Manchester United
OL,9,FFoundation to a primary school pupils
OL,10,Fat Partington Central Academy.
OL,12,FSenne and a group of pupils were
OL,13,Fjoined by children's author A.M. Dassu
OL,14,Fas they took part in The Great Big
OL,15,FWorld Book Day 2026 Footy and Booky
OL,16,FQuiz, a live quiz shared with over
OL,17,Fhalf-a-million children across the
OL,18,Fcountry.
OL,20,FHe said: "I still read a lot today and
OL,21,Fit helps me in football as well.
OL,26,@|D@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
