OL,3,CFrom Harry Potter to SpongeBob see how
OL,4,Cthe North West's marking World Book Day
OL,6,F"One of the great honours we have of
OL,7,Fplaying for Manchester United is the
OL,8,Famount of support we get from our fans
OL,9,Fand especially kids of this age. I
OL,10,Fknow how important it is for them to
OL,11,Fsee guys like us give an example to
OL,12,Fthem and to support them, so it's been
OL,13,Fnice to come and help them and give
OL,14,Fthem some advice."
OL,16,FHere's a selection of the pictures
OL,17,Fsent to us of children all over the
OL,18,FNorth West getting dressed up to
OL,19,Fcelebrate too.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@RO]
