OL,3,CFrom Harry Potter to SpongeBob see how
OL,4,Cthe North West's marking World Book Day
OL,6,FIt's a day relished by creative
OL,7,Fparents and dreaded by others. Matt
OL,8,FBackhouse sent us this fabulous photo
OL,9,Fof his grandchildren Ronny Belfield
OL,10,Fwho's 3, and Betsy Daly aged 8, as
OL,11,FMarge and Homer Simpson. He says their
OL,12,Ftalented mum Sophie Backhouse has
OL,13,Fexcelled again.
OL,15,FIn St Helens Mollie McIntyre had her
OL,16,Fhands full making three costumes for
OL,17,Fher children. She did it in style.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
