OL,3,CFrom Harry Potter to SpongeBob see how
OL,4,Cthe North West's marking World Book Day
OL,6,FHer daughter Evelyn is a book fairy,
OL,7,FCharlie is Optimus Prime the
OL,8,FTransformer and little Alfie is
OL,9,FBumblebee.
OL,11,FIn Nelson in Lancashire, seven year
OL,12,Fold Hareem Shahrukh is Princess Elsa
OL,13,Ffrom Disney hit Frozen and her nine
OL,14,Fyear old brother Finn Azaan Rashid is
OL,15,FFinn from Star Wars.
OL,17,FTheir mum Nyila Parveen said the St
OL,18,FPaul's Primary pupils 'absolutely love
OL,19,Fit'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
