OL,3,CFrom Harry Potter to SpongeBob see how
OL,4,Cthe North West's marking World Book Day
OL,6,FAnd it's not just the children taking
OL,7,Fpart.
OL,9,FAmber Butcher who works at a nursery
OL,10,Fin Blackpool delighted the infants she
OL,11,Fcares for dressing up as Octopus
OL,12,FSocktopus.
OL,14,FShe created the legs with bright socks
OL,15,Fto represent all the octopus legs!
OL,17,FAmber said; "It definitely got plenty
OL,18,Fof smiles and giggles from the
OL,19,Fchildren".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
